{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_001", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 2, "text": "法师学徒凯文在老师的书柜深处发现了一根枯树枝，看起来毫无特别之处。老师却说这是全世界最重要的东西。", "context": "打扫老师书房", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 20, "text": "黑暗军团攻破学院时，凯文拿起那根枯枝挡了一下。枯枝突然绽放出耀眼的光芒，化作一把传说中的法杖——那是创世法树的最后一根枝丫。", "context": "学院被攻破的危急关头", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 18}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_002", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 1, "text": "老国王临终前说的最后一句话是：'王座之下，有光。'所有人以为他在说宗教信仰。", "context": "国王临终遗嘱", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 16, "text": "新国王登基时不小心打翻了王座，地板裂开露出地下密室。密室中存放着大量黄金和一份文件——那是老国王为防备灾年秘密存下的国民救济金。", "context": "王座被意外掀翻时发现密室", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 15}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_003", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 4, "text": "精灵族的弓箭手塞琳娜从来不喝别人给的水，总是自己携带水壶。队友觉得她只是讲究。", "context": "冒险途中的日常", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 30, "text": "塞琳娜的水壶里装的是生命泉水——她是精灵族的末代公主，王室血脉需要定期饮用泉水维持魔力。她隐瞒身份加入冒险团是为了寻找失落的王族神器。", "context": "战斗中水壶被击碎", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 26}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_004", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 5, "text": "城堡花园中有一座没有名字的墓碑，从不允许任何人靠近。园丁说那是'不能问的人'。", "context": "城堡中的禁忌之地", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 25, "text": "墓碑下埋着的是先王的第一位骑士——他因爱上了敌国的女间谍而被处决。先王在他死后才得知那名间谍其实已经背叛了自己的国家，但他已经无法挽回。", "context": "密室中发现先王的忏悔信", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 20}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_005", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 3, "text": "矮人铁匠收到一块来自北地的陨铁，无论怎么加热都无法熔化。他把陨铁扔在了角落。", "context": "铁匠铺日常", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 22, "text": "恶龙来袭时，铁匠拿起陨铁扔向龙口。陨铁在龙炎的高温下终于熔化，化为一柄银白色的战锤。原来龙炎的温度才能激活这块天外陨铁。", "context": "恶龙来袭的危急时刻", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 19}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_006", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 7, "text": "流浪的吟游诗人从不透露自己的全名，只让人叫他'云游者'。他歌唱的旋律古老而忧伤，不像是这个时代的歌。", "context": "酒馆里的表演", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 35, "text": "云游者其实是三百年前失踪的王子，被时光魔法困在了永生之中。他唱的歌都是三百年前的古老民谣，是他唯一能证明自己来历的东西。他的全名是已灭亡王朝的王储。", "context": "古老魔法书中的画像与他一模一样", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 28}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_007", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 8, "text": "魔法学院的顶楼有一座天文钟，钟面上刻着十二个星座。但第十三个位置是空白的，没人知道那里本该是什么。", "context": "学院参观日的讲解", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 40, "text": "第十三个星座是'命运之轮'——学院初代院长用自己的命运为代价，将一次足以毁灭世界的预言灾难推迟了三百年。空白的位置代表他自己，一个不存在于任何记录中的人。", "context": "三百年期满那天天文钟自行运转", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 32}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_008", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 10, "text": "冒险者在沼泽泥潭里捡到一个密封的玻璃瓶，瓶中有一张泛黄的纸条，字迹已经模糊不清了。他随手收进了背包。", "context": "穿越沼泽地的意外发现", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 28, "text": "龙穴中，冒险者被逼到绝境。他不小心打碎了背包里的玻璃瓶，纸条落在地上。纸条上的字在龙息的高温下显现出来——是一张标记着龙命门的藏宝图。", "context": "龙穴中生死一线的时刻", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 18}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_009", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 6, "text": "神殿的预言石碑上写着：'当白鸽飞过火山口，旧王将归来。'大主教说这是古神的启示，但没人能理解。", "context": "神殿礼拜日的布道", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 34, "text": "火山喷发时，漫天的火山灰中有一只白鸽飞过火山口。与此同时，失踪了二十年的王储从火山脚下的洞穴中走出——他当年被政敌推入火山却没有死，被矮人族救下。", "context": "火山喷发时的奇迹景象", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 28}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_010", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 9, "text": "女巫住在森林深处的小屋里，从不邀请任何人进去。村民给她送食物时只能放在门口。", "context": "村民与女巫的日常相处", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 42, "text": "女巫的小屋地下是一个巨大图书馆，收藏着人类王国失传的所有典籍。她守护着这些书，等待一个合适的学者来继承——她的家族世代承担着'守书人'的使命。", "context": "新国王下令烧毁所有魔法书籍", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 33}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_011", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 12, "text": "每个骑士的佩剑上都刻着同一句话：'记住你的名字。'新骑士觉得这只是骑士团的座右铭。", "context": "骑士授剑仪式", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "low"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 38, "text": "这句话的意思是——在战场上杀红眼时，不要忘记自己是谁。老团长在一次战斗中差点误伤友军，这句话救了他。从那以后，每把剑上都刻上了这句话。", "context": "老团长向新骑士讲述往事", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 3}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 26}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_012", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 14, "text": "海底深处有一座沉没的城市，每当满月时分，城中会传出钟声。渔民说那是海妖的歌声。", "context": "渔村的古老传说", "foreshadowing_type": "lore_mystery", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 48, "text": "沉没的城市是上古魔法文明的遗迹。钟声是城市的防御系统，每隔一百年自检一次。城中保存着完整的古代魔法知识，足以改变整个世界的力量格局。", "context": "冒险队潜入海底探索遗迹", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 34}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_013", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 11, "text": "佣兵团里最沉默的战士身上有九道伤疤，每一道都恰好一寸长。他从不提起它们的来历。", "context": "佣兵团篝火夜谈", "foreshadowing_type": "character_secret", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 33, "text": "九道伤疤代表他杀过九个该杀之人——一个叛国的将军、一个虐待奴隶的贵族、一个人贩子头目……他用这种方式记录自己的正义。他不是沉默，而是背负着太多秘密。", "context": "通缉令上的画像揭开了他的真实身份", "resolution_type": "reveal", "satisfaction": 4}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 22}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_014", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 13, "text": "大贤者临终前留下一个预言：'当天空下起蓝色的雨，真正的敌人就会出现。'所有人都以为他在说胡话。", "context": "大贤者葬礼上的悼词", "foreshadowing_type": "prophecy", "subtlety_level": "high"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 50, "text": "龙族入侵时，天空降下了蓝色的雨——那是龙族魔法改变了天气。人们这才明白大贤者的预言不是胡话：蓝色的雨不是灾难的征兆，而是对灾难来源的精确描述。", "context": "龙族来袭时蓝色暴雨倾盆而下", "resolution_type": "callback", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 37}}
{"sample_id": "foreshadow_fantasy_015", "genre": "western_fantasy", "pair_type": "valid_release", "foreshadowing": {"chapter_number": 15, "text": "一个普通的铁戒指在魔法集市上无人问津，因为看起来就是一个普通的铁环。摊主说这是祖传的，要价一百金币。", "context": "集市采购装备", "foreshadowing_type": "object_plot_device", "subtlety_level": "medium"}, "resolution": {"chapter_number": 45, "text": "戴上铁戒指的人在与黑暗法师对决时发现，铁戒指能吸收一切黑暗魔法。这不是普通的铁环，而是用'噬魔铁'打造的——一种只存在于传说中的金属，专门克制黑暗魔法。", "context": "黑暗法师的致命一击被戒指吸收", "resolution_type": "power_up", "satisfaction": 5}, "evaluation": {"foreshadowing_resolution": 1, "plot_continuity": 5, "context_recall": 0.85, "hallucination": 0.1, "is_valid_pair": true, "gap_chapters": 30}}
